{"tid":2101981,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【發射失敗】中国快舟11號運載火箭出現異常 原因有待調查","createTime":"2020-07-10T07:06:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T06:37:19.000Z","uid":184679,"like":126,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"c7f864799faadeecfa761d7b7beabef66b849efd","tid":2101981,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T07:06:09.000Z","msg":"內蒙的酒泉衞星發射中心今日為「快舟11號」運載火箭首次飛行任務，火箭飛行出現異常，發射任務失敗，具體原因有待進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n「快舟11號」也不是首次發射失敗，去年10月，快舟11號火箭發動機試驗台在點火22秒後傳出爆炸聲，現場突然冒出白光與黑煙，整個試驗台和測量設備都被炸成碎片，一片狼藉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200710/N37GUP4G7PNEEJLGNPMTQ4ZLIY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200710%2FN37GUP4G7PNEEJLGNPMTQ4ZLIY%2F&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjvDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=68fd44fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200710%2FN37GUP4G7PNEEJLGNPMTQ4ZLIY%2F&h=fd7dce26\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200710/N37GUP4G7PNEEJLGNPMTQ4ZLIY/</a>"},{"pid":"9b1817780aeb031eb9ee17c233399af56e573a2a","tid":2101981,"uid":41116,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T07:07:26.000Z","msg":"又fail<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"969d6ea444194366e91f4daf0f49b806e9e5a074","tid":2101981,"uid":11578,"like":63,"dislike":0,"score":63,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T07:07:35.000Z","msg":"人地玩緊回收火箭，你仲噴黑煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"138fd20f199a18125b98f52595421240f6bca068","tid":2101981,"uid":237271,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T07:07:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"956f744a58ae6facc8dd20dcbf335c9185ad5c60","tid":2101981,"uid":121146,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T07:11:52.000Z","msg":"唔洗調查  係人都知啦  美國唔賣D晶片比你呀嘛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2